parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sticky steering issue can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially when driving at high speeds or navigating curves.
symptoms: The steering wheel feels sticky or resistant
making it difficult to make small adjustments or turns; the wheel may jerk or lock up
causing the vehicle to swerve or deviate from its intended path; the issue may be more pronounced at high speeds or when driving on curves.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's sudden acceleration and brake application can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates or brakes suddenly without input from the driver
often accompanied by warning lights or messages on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cruise control malfunction can cause unexpected speed changes, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The cruise control shuts off or disengages without warning
often accompanied by a beep or warning message on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The LKAS malfunction can cause the vehicle to drift out of its lane, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The LKAS system fights the driver's input
causing the vehicle to turn or drift out of its lane
often accompanied by warning lights or messages on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Forward Collision Warning and Adaptive Cruise Control Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The forward collision warning and adaptive cruise control malfunction can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving on highways or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The forward collision warning system fails to alert the driver of potential collisions
and the adaptive cruise control system malfunctions
causing unexpected speed changes or braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to slow down or lose speed control, leading to potential accidents or rear-end collisions.
symptoms: Cruise control disengages randomly
unable to reengage
cruise control icon appears on the center display with a beep
cruise control shuts off without warning
requires restarting the vehicle to reengage.

brakes
steering
and automated systems
vehicle runs poorly
dies intermittently

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause loss of control, leading to potential accidents or crashes.
symptoms: Steering wheel locking up
vehicle difficult to steer

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cybersecurity issue can cause unauthorized access to the vehicle's systems, leading to potential safety risks and privacy concerns.
symptoms: Vehicle's audio system hacked
